✅KEEP THE KITCHEN TIDY: The large-capacity drying rack for kitchen sink is designed to store dishes, reduce clutter in the kitchen, and keep your countertop neat. It adopts an all-in-one design that can effectively help you organize various kitchen utensils, tableware and cleaning supplies, such as bowls, plates, knives and forks, cups, cutting boards, spatulas.

✅RUSTPROOF MATERIAL: The over the sink dish drainer drying rack is made of high-quality stainless steel with a smooth black coating on the surface, which is durable enough for long-term use without rust and corrosion.

✅The size of dish rack is 33.5" L X 10" W X 32" H. Fits most kitchen single or double sinks. Please measure your sink size(≤32in), faucet height(≤15in) and countertop-cabinet distance(≥32in) before placing an order.
